msgid ""
"If enabled, all customer’s in the EU will be able to enter a EU VAT number "
"when checking out."
msgstr "如果啟用此功能，歐盟所有客戶在結帳時都可以輸入歐盟增值稅號。"

#: app/Services/Translations/admin-translation.php:839
msgid ""
"If enabled, apply reverse charge when applicable even when customers are in "
"your home country."
msgstr "如果啟用此功能，即使客戶位於您的本國，也應在適用情況下套用反向收費。"

#: app/Services/Translations/admin-translation.php:840
msgid ""
"If set, possible values are duplicate fraudulent, and requested_by_customer "
"If you believe the charge to be fraudulent, specifying fraudulent as the "
"reason will add the associated card and email to your block lists"
msgstr ""
"若已設定，可能的值為 duplicate（重複）、fraudulent（詐欺）和 "
"requested_by_customer（客戶要求）。若您認為此筆款項涉及詐欺，將原因指定為 "
"fraudulent 將把相關卡片和電子郵件加入封鎖名單。如果設定，可選值為「重複詐欺」"
"和「客戶要求」。如果您認為該筆費用是欺詐性的，請將原因指定為「欺詐」，系統會"
"將關聯的銀行卡和電子郵件地址新增到您的黑名單中。"

#: app/Services/Translations/admin-translation.php:842
msgid ""
"If someone replies to your notification email, this is where you would like "
"to\n"
"receive it."
msgstr "如果有人回覆您的通知電子郵件，您希望在此處接收回覆。"

#: app/Services/Translations/admin-translation.php:844
msgid ""
"If you add any prefix here then it will will be used as the prefix of the "
"generated license key"
msgstr "如果在此處新增任何前綴，則該前綴將用作產生的授權金鑰的前綴。"

#: app/Services/Translations/admin-translation.php:845
msgid "If you apply coupon, regular discounts for this order will be removed."
msgstr "如果使用優惠券，則此訂單的常規折扣將被取消。"

#: app/Services/Translations/admin-translation.php:846
msgid ""
"If you don't select any country, all countries will be available for tax "
"calculation. Are you sure you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"若未選擇任何國家，所有國家都將納入稅務計算範圍。確定要繼續嗎？如果您不選擇任"
"何國家/地區，則所有國家/地區都可用於稅金計算。您確定要繼續嗎？"

#: app/Modules/Integrations/FluentPlugins/FluentCommunityConnect.php:151
