"If you enable this, on refund or subscription validity expiration, the "
"selected spaces and courses will be removed from the customer."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，客戶退款或訂閱到期時，將移除所選的空間和課程存取權限。如果啟用此功"
"能，在退款或訂閱有效期到期時，所選名額和課程將從客戶處移除。"

#: app/Modules/Integrations/FluentPlugins/FluentCRMConnect.php:174
