"If you enable this, on refund or subscription validity expiration, the "
"selected tags and lists will be removed from the contact."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，聯絡人退款或訂閱到期時，將移除所選的標籤和名單。如果啟用此功能，在退"
"款或訂閱有效期到期時，所選標籤和清單將從聯絡人中刪除。"

#: app/Modules/Integrations/FluentPlugins/FluentCommunityConnect.php:145
